name: INVERSION LANDSCAPE DIGITAL PAINTING III
description:
INVERSION LANDSCAPE DIGITAL PAINTING III
Our 3D hand sculpted digital painting conceptual art series depicts a unique landscape, that explores spatial qualities of surface. Each digital drawing is an abstract architectural landscape, that was created with a hand sculpting technique as an experiment during the years long research, called project Interface. You get High resolution PDF file ready to print with minimum printable size A3 format. (displayed is a jpeg preview image)
